{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775839923134,"sessionID":"ses_287b1b427ffe9laVG8H8tx72KC","part":{"id":"prt_d784eb8dc001RXHmS8UWaHzSdg","messageID":"msg_d784e9cf6001Geiy3uc4l49RsU","sessionID":"ses_287b1b427ffe9laVG8H8tx72KC","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-33f58d7479424ff6b75de373c66b9f25","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 Proposal\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: Define the Go type structures for `CodeInterpreter` CRD in the `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` package. This CRD provides a specialized sandbox runtime for code execution environments with enhanced features:\n6: \n7: 1. **Warm Pool Management**: Pre-provisioned sandboxes for low-latency startup\n8: 2. **Authentication Integration**: Support for picod auth mode\n9: 3. **Port Exposure**: HTTP/HTTPS endpoints for code interpreter communication\n10: 4. **Resource Management**: CPU/Memory limits for code execution sandboxes\n11: \n12: ## Scope\n13: \n14: ### In Scope\n15: \n16: | Deliverable | Description |\n17: |-------------|-------------|\n18: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go` | Type definitions for CodeInterpreter, CodeInterpreterSpec, CodeInterpreterStatus, CodeInterpreterList |\n19: | Supporting types | CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate, AuthModeType constants, validation markers |\n20: \n21: ### Type Definitions Required\n22: \n23: #### CodeInterpreter\n24: \n25: ```\n26: CodeInterpreter\n27: ├── Spec\n28: │   ├── Ports ([]TargetPort, JSON: ports)\n29: │   ├── Template (*CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate, JSON: template, required)\n30: │   ├── SessionTimeout (*metav1.Duration, default: 15m)\n31: │   ├── MaxSessionDuration (*metav1.Duration, default: 8h)\n32: │   ├── WarmPoolSize (*int32)\n33: │   └── AuthMode (AuthModeType, default: picod, enum: picod|none)\n34: ├── Status\n35: │   ├── Conditions ([]metav1.Condition)\n36: │   └── Ready (*bool)\n37: └── List: CodeInterpreterList\n38: ```\n39: \n40: #### Supporting Types\n41: \n42: - `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate`: Image, command, args, env, resources, runtimeClassName, imagePullPolicy, imagePullSecrets\n43: - `AuthModeType`: Enum for picod/none authentication modes\n44: \n45: ### Out of Scope\n46: \n47: - Controller implementation (`pkg/controllers/`)\n48: - Webhook validation logic\n49: - CRD YAML generation (handled by `make gen-crd`)\n50: - client-go code generation (handled by `make gen-client`)\n51: - AgentRuntime CRD (handled in AR-001)\n52: \n53: ## Impact Analysis\n54: \n55: ### Upstream Dependencies\n56: \n57: | Dependency | Impact |\n58: |------------|--------|\n59: | `k8s.io/apimachinery` | Required for metav1.ObjectMeta, metav1.Duration, metav1.Condition |\n60: | `k8s.io/api/corev1` | Required for PodSpec elements (EnvVar, PullPolicy, ResourceRequirements) |\n61: \n62: ### Downstream Consumers\n63: \n64: | Consumer | Usage |\n65: |----------|-------|\n66: | `make gen-crd` | Generates CRD YAML to `manifests/charts/base/crds/` |\n67: | `make gen-client` | Generates typed clients, informers, listers |\n68: | Workload Manager | Creates Sandbox/SandboxClaim instances from CodeInterpreter specs |\n69: | Router | Routes code interpreter requests to appropriate sandboxes |\n70: \n71: ## Risks\n72: \n73: | Risk | Mitigation |\n74: |------|------------|\n75: | Warm pool size validation | Consider webhook for min/max values |\n76: | AuthMode enum changes | Pin enum values in design doc |\n77: | Status field extensions | Reserve fields for future use |\n78: \n79: ## Implementation Notes\n80: \n81: 1. **Boilerplate**: Use `hack/boilerplate.go.txt` header\n82: 2. **JSON Tags**: camelCase per project conventions\n83: 3. **Kubebuilder Markers**: Apply validation markers for required fields and enums\n84: 4. **Printer Columns**: Add Age column for `kubectl get` output\n85: \n86: ## References\n87: \n88: - Kubernetes API Conventions: https://git.k8s.io/community/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md\n89: - Kubebuilder Book: https://book.kubebuilder.io/\n\n(End of file - total 89 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 Proposal\n\n## Purpose\n\nDefine the Go type structures for `CodeInterpreter` CRD in the `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` package. This CRD provides a specialized sandbox runtime for code execution environments with enhanced features:\n\n1. **Warm Pool Management**: Pre-provisioned sandboxes for low-latency startup\n2. **Authentication Integration**: Support for picod auth mode\n3. **Port Exposure**: HTTP/HTTPS endpoints for code interpreter communication\n4. **Resource Management**: CPU/Memory limits for code execution sandboxes\n\n## Scope\n\n### In Scope\n\n| Deliverable | Description |\n|-------------|-------------|\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go` | Type definitions for CodeInterpreter, CodeInterpreterSpec, CodeInterpreterStatus, CodeInterpreterList |\n| Supporting types | CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate, AuthModeType constants, validation markers |\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775839923108,"end":1775839923132}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775839923135,"sessionID":"ses_287b1b427ffe9laVG8H8tx72KC","part":{"id":"prt_d784ebd38001KB7mvD3u2Ods9w","messageID":"msg_d784e9cf6001Geiy3uc4l49RsU","sessionID":"ses_287b1b427ffe9laVG8H8tx72KC","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-0e627dbe0f704934905c5dffbfd281fd","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义\n2: \n3: ## Metadata\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/apis` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | S |\n11: | Stage | ST-0 |\n12: \n13: ## Scope\n14: \n15: 定义 CodeInterpreter CRD 的 Go 类型结构，包括:\n16: - `CodeInterpreter` 类型及其 `Spec`、`Status`\n17: - `CodeInterpreterList` 类型\n18: - `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` 类型\n19: - `AuthModeType` 枚举及常量定义\n20: \n21: ## Out of Scope\n22: \n23: - Controller 实现\n24: - Webhook 验证逻辑\n25: - CRD YAML 生成\n26: - client-go 代码生成\n27: - AgentRuntime CRD（已在 AR-001 中定义）\n28: \n29: ## Dependencies\n30: \n31: 依赖 AR-001 中定义的共享类型：\n32: - `TargetPort`\n33: - `ProtocolType`\n34: \n35: ## Deliverables\n36: \n37: | File | Description |\n38: |------|-------------|\n39: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go` | CodeInterpreter 类型定义 |\n40: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` | AuthModeType 等共享类型（如需新增） |\n41: \n42: ## Acceptance Criteria\n43: \n44: - [ ] 类型定义符合 Kubernetes API conventions\n45: - [ ] JSON tags 使用 camelCase\n46: - [ ] 包含完整的字段注释\n47: - [ ] 通过 `go vet` 和 `golangci-lint`\n48: - [ ] Enum 验证标记正确\n49: \n50: ## References\n51: \n52: - Kubernetes API Conventions: https://git.k8s.io/community/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md\n53: - AR-001 Design: `changes/AR-001/design.md`\n\n(End of file - total 53 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/apis` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-0 |\n\n## Scope\n\n定义 CodeInterpreter CRD 的 Go 类型结构，包括:\n- `CodeInterpreter` 类型及其 `Spec`、`Status`\n- `CodeInterpreterList` 类型\n- `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` 类型\n- `AuthModeType` 枚举及常量定义\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/spec.md","time":{"start":1775839923111,"end":1775839923134}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775839923137,"sessionID":"ses_287b1b427ffe9laVG8H8tx72KC","part":{"id":"prt_d784ec1e1001F0s3m8orz5towj","messageID":"msg_d784e9cf6001Geiy3uc4l49RsU","sessionID":"ses_287b1b427ffe9laVG8H8tx72KC","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-ba0ff123302549ff881b4da324e6ca75","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-002/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 Design\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/apis` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | S |\n11: | Stage | ST-1 |\n12: \n13: 定义 CodeInterpreter CRD 的 Go 类型结构，用于代码解释器沙箱运行时。API group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`。\n14: \n15: ## Design\n16: \n17: ### Architecture\n18: \n19: CodeInterpreter CRD 类型定义遵循 Kubernetes API conventions：\n20: - 使用 `kubebuilder` markers 生成 OpenAPI schema\n21: - 类型定义与 DeepCopy 代码分离，由 controller-gen 自动生成\n22: - 支持 status subresource，用于控制器更新资源状态\n23: - Namespaced scope，每个命名空间内独立管理代码解释器实例\n24: \n25: ### Dependencies\n26: \n27: | Package | Purpose |\n28: |---------|---------|\n29: | `k8s.io/api/core/v1` | EnvVar、PullPolicy、ResourceRequirements、LocalObjectReference |\n30: | `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1` | TypeMeta、ObjectMeta、Condition、Duration |\n31: | `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema` | GroupVersion、GroupVersionResource |\n32: \n33: ### Controller-gen Markers\n34: \n35: | Marker | Applied to | Purpose |\n36: |--------|------------|---------|\n37: | `+kubebuilder:object:root=true` | Main type + List type | 注册到 Scheme |\n38: | `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` | Main type | 启用 status subresource |\n39: | `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced` | Main type | 命名空间级别资源 |\n40: | `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\"` | Main type | kubectl 输出列 |\n41: | `+genclient` | Main type | 生成 typed client |\n42: | `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=...` | Main type + List type | DeepCopy 接口 |\n43: \n44: ## Data Structures\n45: \n46: ### CodeInterpreter Types\n47: \n48: ```go\n49: // +genclient\n50: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n51: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n52: // +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n53: // +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced\n54: // +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\n55: type CodeInterpreter struct {\n56:     metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n57:     metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n58:     Spec   CodeInterpreterSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n59:     Status CodeInterpreterStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n60: }\n61: \n62: type CodeInterpreterSpec struct {\n63:     // +optional\n64:     Ports []TargetPort `json:\"ports,omitempty\"`\n65:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n66:     Template *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate `json:\"template\"`\n67:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"\n68:     SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\"`\n69:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"\n70:     MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\"`\n71:     // +optional\n72:     WarmPoolSize *int32 `json:\"warmPoolSize,omitempty\"`\n73:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"picod\"\n74:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=picod;none\n75:     // +optional\n76:     AuthMode AuthModeType `json:\"authMode,omitempty\"`\n77: }\n78: \n79: type CodeInterpreterStatus struct {\n80:     // +optional\n81:     Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n82:     // +optional\n83:     Ready bool `json:\"ready,omitempty\"`\n84: }\n85: \n86: type CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate struct {\n87:     // +optional\n88:     Labels map[string]string `json:\"labels,omitempty\"`\n89:     // +optional\n90:     Annotations map[string]string `json:\"annotations,omitempty\"`\n91:     // +optional\n92:     RuntimeClassName *string `json:\"runtimeClassName,omitempty\"`\n93:     Image string `json:\"image,omitempty\"`\n94:     // +optional\n95:     ImagePullPolicy corev1.PullPolicy `json:\"imagePullPolicy,omitempty\"`\n96:     // +optional\n97:     // +patchMergeKey=name\n98:     // +patchStrategy=merge\n99:     // +listType=map\n100:     // +listMapKey=name\n101:     ImagePullSecrets []corev1.LocalObjectReference `json:\"imagePullSecrets,omitempty\"`\n102:     // +optional\n103:     Environment []corev1.EnvVar `json:\"environment,omitempty\"`\n104:     // +optional\n105:     // +listType=atomic\n106:     Command []string `json:\"command,omitempty\"`\n107:     // +optional\n108:     Args []string `json:\"args,omitempty\"`\n109:     // +optional\n110:     Resources corev1.ResourceRequirements `json:\"resources,omitempty\"`\n111: }\n112: \n113: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n114: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n115: type CodeInterpreterList struct {\n116:     metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n117:     metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n118:     Items           []CodeInterpreter `json:\"items\"`\n119: }\n120: ```\n121: \n122: ### Shared Types\n123: \n124: ```go\n125: type AuthModeType string\n126: \n127: const (\n128:     AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n129:     AuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n130: )\n131: ```\n132: \n133: ## API Schema\n134: \n135: ### CRD OpenAPI Constraints\n136: \n137: | Resource | Required Spec Fields |\n138: |----------|----------------------|\n139: | CodeInterpreter | `template` |\n140: \n141: ### Defaults\n142: \n143: | Field | Default Value |\n144: |-------|---------------|\n145: | `sessionTimeout` | `15m` |\n146: | `maxSessionDuration` | `8h` |\n147: | `authMode` | `picod` |\n148: | `ports[].protocol` | `HTTP` |\n149: \n150: ### Enums\n151: \n152: | Field | Allowed Values |\n153: |-------|----------------|\n154: | `authMode` | `picod`, `none` |\n155: \n156: ### REST Resource Plural\n157: \n158: | Kind | Plural |\n159: |------|--------|\n160: | CodeInterpreter | `codeinterpreters` |\n161: \n162: ### Printer Columns\n163: \n164: | Name | Type | JSONPath |\n165: |------|------|----------|\n166: | Age | date | `.metadata.creationTimestamp` |\n167: \n168: ## Error Handling\n169: \n170: - 缺少必填字段 `template` 时，API server 拒绝创建请求\n171: - 无效 enum 值时，API server 返回 validation error\n172: - Duration 格式错误时，使用 Go `metav1.Duration` 解析失败抛出错误\n173: \n174: ## Testing Strategy\n175: \n176: ### Unit Tests\n177: \n178: | Test Category | Coverage |\n179: |---------------|----------|\n180: | DeepCopy generation | 确保 DeepCopy 方法正确复制所有字段 |\n181: | Default values | 验证 kubebuilder 默认值标记生效 |\n182: | Enum validation | 测试 `authMode` 所有允许值及无效值 |\n183: | JSON serialization | 验证 JSON tag 正确映射 |\n184: \n185: ### Integration Tests\n186: \n187: - CRD 安装验证：确保 `make gen-crd` 生成的 YAML 可被 k8s API server 接受\n188: - Client-go 生成验证：`make gen-client` 生成的 client/informer/lister 可正常使用\n189: \n190: ## File Structure\n191: \n192: ```\n193: pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n194:   codeinterpreter_types.go — CodeInterpreter、CodeInterpreterList、CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate\n195:   shared_types.go           — AuthModeType 常量（如需新增）\n196: ```\n197: \n198: ## Generation Commands\n199: \n200: | Command | Output |\n201: |---------|--------|\n202: | `make generate` | DeepCopy 代码 + CRD YAML |\n203: | `make gen-client` | client-go（clientset、informers、listers） |\n204: \n205: ## References\n206: \n207: - Source: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n208: - client-go: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/client-go/`\n209: - controller-tools version: `v0.17.2`\n\n(End of file - total 209 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/apis