 **T1.2** Define `CodeInterpreterStatus`\n37:   - `Conditions []metav1.Condition` (optional)\n38:   - `Ready bool` (optional)\n39:   - Verify: `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n40: \n41: - [ ] **T1.3** Define `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate`\n42:   - `Labels map[string]string`\n43:   - `Annotations map[string]string`\n44:   - `RuntimeClassName *string`\n45:   - `Image string`\n46:   - `ImagePullPolicy corev1.PullPolicy`\n47:   - `ImagePullSecrets []corev1.LocalObjectReference`\n48:   - `Environment []corev1.EnvVar`\n49:   - `Command []string`\n50:   - `Args []string`\n51:   - `Resources corev1.ResourceRequirements`\n52:   - Verify: `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n53: \n54: - [ ] **T1.4** Define `CodeInterpreterList`\n55:   - Add markers: `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces`, `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`\n56:   - Verify: `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n57: \n58: ### Phase 2: Shared Types\n59: \n60: - [ ] **T2.1** Create or update `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go`\n61:   - Define `AuthModeType string`\n62:   - Define constants:\n63:     - `AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"`\n64:     - `AuthModeNone AuthModeType = \"none\"`\n65:   - Verify: `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n66: \n67: ### Phase 3: Code Generation\n68: \n69: - [ ] **T3.1** Run `controller-gen object paths=./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...`\n70:   - Verify: `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` includes CodeInterpreter types\n71:   - Verify: All types implement `runtime.Object` interface\n72: \n73: - [ ] **T3.2** Run `controller-gen crd paths=./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... output:crd:dir=manifests/charts/base/crds`\n74:   - Verify: `codeinterpreters` CRD YAML generated\n75: \n76: - [ ] **T3.3** Run `client-gen` to generate client-go code\n77:   - Verify: CodeInterpreter client generated in `client-go/`\n78: \n79: ### Phase 4: Unit Tests\n80: \n81: - [ ] **T4.1** Create or update `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go`\n82:   - Test DeepCopy for `CodeInterpreter`\n83:   - Test default values: `sessionTimeout=15m`, `maxSessionDuration=8h`, `authMode=picod`\n84:   - Test enum validation for `AuthModeType`\n85:   - Test JSON serialization/deserialization\n86:   - Verify: `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... -v`\n87: \n88: ### Phase 5: Validation & Quality\n89: \n90: - [ ] **T5.1** Run `go vet ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...`\n91:   - Fix any issues reported\n92: \n93: - [ ] **T5.2** Run `golangci-lint run ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...`\n94:   - Fix any linting issues\n95: \n96: - [ ] **T5.3** Verify JSON tags use camelCase\n97:   - Check: `ports`, `template`, `sessionTimeout`, `maxSessionDuration`, `warmPoolSize`, `authMode`\n98:   - Check: `imagePullPolicy`, `imagePullSecrets`, `environment`\n99: \n100: - [ ] **T5.4** Verify Kubernetes API conventions compliance\n101:   - Required fields have `+kubebuilder:validation:Required` marker\n102:   - Optional fields have `+optional` marker\n103:   - Default values specified with `+kubebuilder:default=...`\n104: \n105: ### Phase 6: Documentation\n106: \n107: - [ ] **T6.1** Add godoc comments to all exported types and fields\n108: - [ ] **T6.2** Verify package-level documentation describes CodeInterpreter purpose\n109: \n110: ---\n111: \n112: ## Task Dependencies\n113: \n114: ```\n115: T1.1 → T1.2 → T1.3 → T1.4\n116:                       ↓\n117:                     T2.1\n118:                       ↓\n119:                     T3.1 → T3.2 → T3.3\n120:                                      ↓\n121:                                    T4.1\n122:                                      ↓\n123:                       T5.1 → T5.2 → T5.3 → T5.4\n124:                                      ↓\n125:                                    T6.1 → T6.2\n126: ```\n127: \n128: ---\n129: \n130: ## Verification Commands\n131: \n132: | Task | Verification Command |\n133: |------|----------------------|\n134: | T1.1-T1.4, T2.1 | `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...` |\n135: | T3.1 | `grep -q \"CodeInterpreter\" pkg